        p Rebuilt non-profit organization website on WordPress, reevaluated and modified all pages for improved usability and SEO. Created custom post types archive pages and added pagination to custom post types archive pages. Created custom post types and custom taxonomies.Migrated website from subdomain to main domain. Added MailChimp signup form to WordPress website without a plugin. Created email account in the cPanel. Managed the website from front end to back end.
      ul.portfolio__buttons
        li
          a.demo(href="https://apex.org" target="_blank") View Website
  .projectTwo#projectTwo
    a(href="https://now-thatsdelicious.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank")
      img.portfolio__img(src="./assets/img/nowThatsDelicious.gif" alt="Now That's Delicious")
    .portfolio__about
      h4 Title
        span Now That's Delicious 
      h4 Tools
        span HTML, CSS, Javascript, Node.js, Express.js, Passport.js, MongoDB
